#+TAGS:


* udevadm
* Description
This is the utility provided by udev to manage devices device nodes in a system.
* Usage
- monitor udev activity
#+BEGIN_SRC sh
udevadm monitor
#+END_SRC
this will now show on screen any activity that udev performs
to test this run the cmd and add a usb device all of udev actions will be seen

